title: 在启动minecraft时出现需要下载Baubles-1.7.10-1.0.1.10.jar该怎么解决？
author: 中国用户
txt_content:
这该怎么办啊！
     CB's DepLoader was unable to download required library     Baubles-1.7.10-1.0.1.10.jar
Check your internet connection and try     restarting or download it manually from
https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/47135879//Baubles-1.7.10-1.0.1.10.jar     and put it in your mods folder

游戏版本为1.7.10  
forge版本为1.7.10-10.13.4.1614-1.7.10

replies.author: A55778866579
replies.txt_content:
可能是你游戏中的某个mod需要 饰品栏Baubles mod

我帮你下载下来了

https://cowtransfer.com/s/890cc6f62ae547

把里面的.jar文件放进mods里面就好了
